<HEADLINE>
<P>
NRA AND SECOND AMENDMENT 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
This is a letter to National Rifle Assn. members: 
</P>
<P>
You keep talking about the Second Amendment. 
</P>
<P>
I hate to tell you fellows, but none of today's guns are covered by the Second 
Amendment. 
</P>
<P>
Now, if you have a single-shot cap and ball pistol or a single-shot, 
muzzle-loading rifle you're covered. Anything else is not covered. 
</P>
<P>
These were the guns the Second Amendment was written for; that's all there were 
in those days. Too bad. 
</P>
<P>
RON EKARD 
</P>
<P>
Laguna Hills 
</P>
</TEXT>
