before his enraged, eighth-inning public address. Associated Press; Photo, 
Willie McCovey, as Padre player representative in 1974, accepted Ray Kroc's 
apology to the team.; Photo, Doug Rader's comments about Padre owner Ray Kroc 
inspired the "Short-Order Cooks' Night" promotion. ; Photo, President Buzzie 
Bavasi, on Ray Kroc's comments: "He regretted saying it, but there was nothing 
he could do." ; Photo, Ray A. Kroc 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
