CRIME STATISTICS; SANTA MONICA (CA) -- GOVERNMENT OFFICIALS; SANTA MONICA (CA) 
-- GOVERNMENT; WELFARE PROGRAMS -- LOS ANGELES COUNTY; COMMUNITY SERVICE 
PROGRAMS; VIOLENCE 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
