<TEXT>
<P>
Kirk Gibson, who suffered a strained groin muscle while running out a single 
Monday, was out of the lineup Tuesday. 
</P>
<P>
Gibson was examined Tuesday by Dr. Ralph Gambardella, who confirmed the strain. 
</P>
