VALENCIA'S SWAIL AN ALL-AMERICAN IN WATER POLO 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Julie Swail, a junior at Valencia High School, has been named an All-American 
in water polo by the National Interscholastic Swimming Coaches of America. 
