<P>
Mattel Sued for Cleanup Costs: A $1.4-million lawsuit was filed against Mattel 
Inc. by H&amp;H Paramount, a Los Angeles limited partnership, which claims that 
the toy maker "actively concealed" its use and disposal of hazardous waste at a 
plastic molding plant in Paramount. 
</P>
<P>
